title: War of the Roses: Another Woman is Paying for His Cell Phone
description: Linda is calling in to try to catch her best friend's boyfriend cheating.  He sent a text to his girlfriend but called her a different girl's name in the text.  He's also cheated before.  Signs point to yes he's cheating again but we'll see on War of the Roses!
